FILES & DIRS
------------
- package.json    - main npm configuration
- config.json     - basic configuraiton file
- keys/           - SSL certs for local/dev site
- src/config/     - configuration reader and helpers
- src/index.js    - main entry point
- src/subscruber/ - subscriber services module
- src/mailer/     - smtp services module
- src/template.js - template module
- src/template/   - HTML templates (*.ejs)

